cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

This paper deals with computer vision algorithms and image processing techniques to remove reflections from images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves generating synthetic data, which falls under the category of computer graphics (cs.GR). The use of deep learning algorithms suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves image processing techniques, which could also fall under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
